Pilot artifacts go here once Phase 3 begins.

Suggested subdirs (created when needed):
- consent-forms/         (templates — signed copies in pilot/consent-signed/, gitignored)
- interview-guides/      (semi-structured interview scripts, EN + FR)
- recruitment/           (flyers, contact lists with PII redacted)
- transcripts/           (audio transcripts, gitignored)
- analysis/              (thematic coding, SUS scoring, summary plots)
- raw_responses/         (questionnaire exports, gitignored)
